Add new methods to ModelManager and corresponding tests
commitResults.messageBody:
This commit adds the following methods to ModelManager:
- getPersonByName(String name): Retrieves the person with the given name from the model.
- addMeeting(Meeting meeting): Adds a new meeting to the model.
- hasMeeting(Meeting meeting): Returns true if the model contains the given meeting.

In addition, corresponding tests have been added to the ModelManagerTest class to ensure these methods are working as expected.

commitResults.messageBody:
This commit adds the following methods to Model:
- getPersonByName(String name): Retrieves the person with the given name from the model.
- addMeeting(Meeting meeting): Adds a new meeting to the model.
- hasMeeting(Meeting meeting): Returns true if the model contains the given meeting.

This commit adds the following Prefixes to CliSyntax:
- PREFIX_MEETING_TITLE - m/
- PREFIX_DATE - d/
- PREFIX_LOCATION - l/
- PREFIX_DESCRIPTION - des/
- PREFIX_PERSON - p/
